section.article:
X.C.VIII.005 Constituent chemicals for propellants as follows:
Toluene Diisocyanate, in any isomeric form (CAS 584-84-9, 91-08-7, 26471-62-5, 9002-68-2, 26628-22-8);
Methyl Diphenyl Diisocyanate (CAS 101-68-8);
Isophorone Diisocyanate (CAS 4098-71-9);
Xylidine in any isomeric form (CAS 87-59-2, 95-68-1, 95-78-3, 87-62-7, 95-63-6 or 108-69-0);
Hydroxy Terminated Polyether (HTPE);
Hydroxy Terminated Caprolactone Ether (HTCE).
